How To Buy 

Buying Crypto All-Stars is super easy, even if you've never bought meme coins before!

Create Your Wallet If you use a PC, install a MetaMask wallet browser extension - this is where your $STARS will be stored. Prefer mobile? Download Best Wallet for the easiest setup. There are other wallets, so if you've already got one, click the Wallet Connect button to check compatibility.

Get Some Crypto If you're paying with a card, you can skip this step. If not, grab some crypto (check the buy widget for all accepted cryptocurrencies). This can be done on centralized exchanges like Coinbase, Binance, Kraken or all others!

Connect Wallet + Buy Click the BUY NOW button anywhere on this website to connect your wallet. Doing so will unlock the Buy Widget where you can then select how much $STARS you want and your payment method. Select Buy and Stake to earn rewards! Only staking will earn you rewards.
